### Initiate GitHub OAuth Flow (Redirect)
# You need to open this URL in your actual WEB BROWSER to start the flow.
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/github HTTP/1.1




### GitHub OAuth Callback Endpoint
# GitHub redirects the user's BROWSER here after authorization,
# automatically including a temporary 'code' in the query parameters.
# Example URL GitHub would redirect to:  http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/github/callback?code=SOME_TEMPORARY_CODE_FROM_GITHUB
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/github/callback HTTP/1.1